<div align="center"><span style="font-size: 16pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>Activando la barra lateral (widgets)</strong></span></div><br />En <strong>functions.php</strong>, agregar:<br /><br /><div class="codeheader">Código: <a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="return smfSelectText(this);" class="codeoperation">[Seleccionar]</a></div><code class="bbc_code"><span style="color: #000000"><span style="color: #0000BB">&lt;?php<br /></span><span style="color: #FF8000">//&nbsp;De&nbsp;nuevo,&nbsp;el&nbsp;nombre&nbsp;de&nbsp;esta&nbsp;función&nbsp;es&nbsp;personalizable<br /></span><span style="color: #007700">function&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #0000BB">myfcn_register_sidebars</span><span style="color: #007700">()&nbsp;{<br /><br /></span><span style="color: #0000BB">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #0000BB">register_sidebars</span><span style="color: #007700">(array(<br /></span><span style="color: #0000BB">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #0000BB">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #DD0000">&#039;name&#039;&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #007700">=&gt;&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #0000BB">__</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">&#039;Sidebar&nbsp;principal&#039;</span><span style="color: #007700">,&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #DD0000">&#039;apk&#039;</span><span style="color: #007700">),&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #FF8000">//&nbsp;&#039;apk&#039;&nbsp;es&nbsp;solo&nbsp;un&nbsp;ejemplo,&nbsp;ahí&nbsp;debe&nbsp;ir&nbsp;el&nbsp;dato&nbsp;introducido&nbsp;en&nbsp;la&nbsp;cabecera&nbsp;del&nbsp;archivo&nbsp;style.css,&nbsp;en&nbsp;el&nbsp;campo&nbsp;"Text&nbsp;Domain:"<br /></span><span style="color: #0000BB">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #0000BB">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #DD0000">&#039;id&#039;&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #007700">=&gt;&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #DD0000">&#039;main_sidebar&#039;</span><span style="color: #007700">,<br /></span><span style="color: #0000BB">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #0000BB">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #DD0000">&#039;description&#039;&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #007700">=&gt;&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #0000BB">__</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">&#039;Este&nbsp;es&nbsp;el&nbsp;sidebar&nbsp;principal&#039;</span><span style="color: #007700">,&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #DD0000">&#039;apk&#039;</span><span style="color: #007700">),<br /></span><span style="color: #0000BB">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #0000BB">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #DD0000">&#039;before_widget&#039;&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #007700">=&gt;&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #DD0000">&#039;&lt;div&nbsp;id="%1$s"&nbsp;class="widget&nbsp;%2$s"&gt;&#039;</span><span style="color: #007700">,&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #FF8000">//&nbsp;aqui&nbsp;puede&nbsp;ir&nbsp;el&nbsp;tag&nbsp;que&nbsp;desees&nbsp;con&nbsp;los&nbsp;parámetros&nbsp;que&nbsp;desees,&nbsp;sin&nbsp;embargo,&nbsp;wp&nbsp;te&nbsp;ofrece&nbsp;la&nbsp;convención&nbsp;%1$s&nbsp;y&nbsp;%2$s&nbsp;para&nbsp;que&nbsp;de&nbsp;ese&nbsp;modo&nbsp;puedas&nbsp;darle&nbsp;un&nbsp;id&nbsp;único&nbsp;a&nbsp;cada&nbsp;elemento<br /></span><span style="color: #0000BB">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #0000BB">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #DD0000">&#039;after_widget&#039;&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #007700">=&gt;&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #DD0000">&#039;&lt;/div&gt;&#039;</span><span style="color: #007700">,<br /></span><span style="color: #0000BB">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #0000BB">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #DD0000">&#039;before_title&#039;&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #007700">=&gt;&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #DD0000">&#039;&lt;h3&nbsp;class="widget-title"&gt;&#039;</span><span style="color: #007700">,<br /></span><span style="color: #0000BB">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #0000BB">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #DD0000">&#039;after_title&#039;&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #007700">=&gt;&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #DD0000">&#039;&lt;/h3&gt;&#039;<br /></span><span style="color: #0000BB">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;));<br /><br />}<br /></span><span style="color: #0000BB">add_action</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">&#039;widgets_init&#039;</span><span style="color: #007700">,&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #DD0000">&#039;myfcn_register_sidebars&#039;</span><span style="color: #007700">);</span></span></code><br />Luego, en <strong>sidebar.php</strong>:<br /><br /><div class="codeheader">Código: <a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="return smfSelectText(this);" class="codeoperation">[Seleccionar]</a></div><code class="bbc_code">&lt;aside id=&quot;sidebar&quot;&gt;<br /><br />&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style="color: #000000"><span style="color: #0000BB">&lt;?php&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #007700">if&nbsp;(&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #0000BB">is_active_sidebar</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">&#039;main_sidebar&#039;</span><span style="color: #007700">)&nbsp;)&nbsp;{<br /><br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #0000BB">dynamic_sidebar</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">&#039;main_sidebar&#039;</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br /><br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #0000BB">?&gt;</span></span><br /><br />&lt;/aside&gt;</code><br />Alternativamente puedes hacer ésto para que se muestre algo en el sidebar por defecto en lugar de verse vacío en caso de que el usuario decida no insertar ningún widget:<br /><br /><div class="codeheader">Código: <a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="return smfSelectText(this);" class="codeoperation">[Seleccionar]</a></div><code class="bbc_code">&lt;aside id=&quot;sidebar&quot;&gt;<br /><br />&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style="color: #000000"><span style="color: #0000BB">&lt;?php&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #007700">if&nbsp;(&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #0000BB">is_active_sidebar</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">&#039;main_sidebar&#039;</span><span style="color: #007700">)&nbsp;)&nbsp;{<br /><br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #0000BB">dynamic_sidebar</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">&#039;main_sidebar&#039;</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br /><br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;else&nbsp;{&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #0000BB">?&gt;</span></span><br /><br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;div class=&quot;widget&quot;&gt;<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;h3 class=&quot;widget-title&quot;&gt;<span style="color: #000000"><span style="color: #0000BB">&lt;?php&nbsp;_e</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">&#039;Buscar&#039;</span><span style="color: #007700">,&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #DD0000">&#039;apk&#039;</span><span style="color: #007700">);&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #0000BB">?&gt;</span></span>&lt;/h3&gt;<br /><br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span style="color: #000000"><span style="color: #0000BB">&lt;?php&nbsp;get_search_form</span><span style="color: #007700">();&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #0000BB">?&gt;</span></span><br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;/div&gt;<br /><br />&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style="color: #000000"><span style="color: #0000BB">&lt;?php&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #007700">}&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #0000BB">?&gt;</span></span><br /><br />&lt;/aside&gt;</code>
